com.ualberta.cmput301w17t22.moodswing

Class ApprovalList

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ualberta.cmput301w17t22.moodswing.ApprovalList

  • public class ApprovalList
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains two lists of usernames of Participants. Participants username are initially added as "pending". After approval, Participants are promoted to "approved". This list is part-of Participant (implemented twice).
    Version:
    2017-03-03
    Author:
    Fred
    See Also:
    Participant

        public void newPendingParticipant(Participant otherParticipant)

        Method takes in a participant that the mainParticipant needs to add to the pending list. If the participant is already in the pending or approved lists then an exception is thrown. Otherwise it adds that participants username to the pending list.
